{"tid":2257404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國推數字化人民幣 盼避美制裁","createTime":"2020-10-25T06:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T14:00:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9d1eb9479e32e5c3c3b3e0d9e71916ae5cb08a","tid":2257404,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:38:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201025/J4AVI5PSGJGCTH3YL3JHQ62RRY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201025%2FJ4AVI5PSGJGCTH3YL3JHQ62RRY%2F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=951d146a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201025%2FJ4AVI5PSGJGCTH3YL3JHQ62RRY%2F&h=4802f914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201025/J4AVI5PSGJGCTH3YL3JHQ62RRY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中國推數字化人民幣 盼避美制裁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p6wOJCpZuhX2Wx5jXCx9y_oqAHs=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XE4SQV6YJZAYFJSSXRUDDMCLJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp6wOJCpZuhX2Wx5jXCx9y_oqAHs%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXE4SQV6YJZAYFJSSXRUDDMCLJU.jpg&h=abc63945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中國將立法推動數字貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n央行前晚公佈人民銀行積極推進《中華人民共和國中國人民銀行法》修改工作，現希望徵求意見，其中「人民幣」章節提到規定以實物形式和數字形式發放人民幣，官方首次欲為數字貨幣提供法律依據。美國克林信大學經濟系副教授徐家健向本報分析，人民幣數字化長遠或可避過美國利用Swift系統的經濟制裁，有利以人民幣結算。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n監控金流助打擊洗錢<br />\n<br />\n今次徵求意見分為九章，包括組織機構、人民幣、監督管理職責及法律等。職責就表明由國務院及中國人民銀行負責，在「人民幣」章節，除了表明要為數字貨幣提供法律依據，亦明確指出任何單位和個人不得製作、發售代幣票券和數字代幣。<br />\n<br />\n徐家健指出，人民幣數字化對中國最大好處是「控制到貨幣流通」，知道金錢的流向，有助監控及打擊洗黑錢。資金的流向亦會成為大數據，有助官。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，中國亦有權凍結一些國內政敵或異見人士，進一步打壓人權。<br />\n<br />\n人民網/《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"bc6552c27b8fe42610260fc0fbcce145452f75a2","tid":2257404,"uid":275238,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:39:52.000Z","msg":"好似冥幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbbe37062c24007661be2ed90d6960e3c2bb02ec","tid":2257404,"uid":153811,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec3f224abbb1f6cc4db8f99981ac48b0275ab5e","tid":2257404,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:59:37.000Z","msg":"聽落幾勁咁<br />\n唔係話做交易一定用swift?<br />\n咁就避到？<br />\n有人講解下原理？"},{"pid":"c814bb7fd5a032472da63927fee57e4c2441858c","tid":2257404,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"聽埋呢度就會知多少少 work 唔 work<br />\n<br />\n吳明德 數字貨幣如果成功，可以同美元脫鉤 /  Fox News老闆說拜登會大勝 /  美國貿易逆差可否用來攻擊特朗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2257405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2257405</a>"},{"pid":"d22928c2b1b7e395385f3586be6d6d9ccf2ce2d7","tid":2257404,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T07:01:49.000Z","msg":"聽佢咁講777都用到payme噃"},{"pid":"c0527d69846829e1eb9fe51e741f673d2a025968","tid":2257404,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T07:06:58.000Z","msg":"成篇野都係由一隻共狗轉貼人民網嘅飛機文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150cf3dce9f589feb1d54f265174bfea65832030","tid":2257404,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"咪即係軍票，換唔返現實世界嘅錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d808a7a8192146996c94d6877aa4ccc3e185e6ef","tid":2257404,"uid":143499,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T07:14:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"632bf440028f10c039419c6ccbd557ceb76c8979","tid":2257404,"uid":31215,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2